data.name: SAFETY BLOOD LANCETS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- Polypropylene (PP)
- Stainless Steel

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Color-Coded Size Identification
- Regulated Spring Activation Concept

## PERFORMANCE
- Easy Activation Safety Mechanism
- inviolable closure technology
- Electronic bevel and 100% medical grade stainless steel needle
- Smooth Surface while outstanding Grip
- Low Pain experience
